| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2601 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0e182304-2e3f-515a-84fc-db1ebdd342bc"
